text:
Surf Ave., (rear view), south side, between Jones Walk and West 10th Street. This is a view of Feltman's Restaurant, pavilion and bathhouse, showing a part of the Beach and Surf Ave., in the early 1870'.
About 1875.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
